Advantages
-Free and Open source
-Supports Java, Phyton, PHP, C# etc.
-Supports all browsers
-Works on all OSz

Disadvantages
-We can use just for web based applications but with Appium we can use for mobile applications
-Selenium is not a company that is why doesn't have professional support
-We can not do performance testing
-We can not automate captcha

How we can do Test Automation ?
We use Webdriver libary with Selenium Library
Also we need Maven build ----> Pom.xml

Maven ---> Build tool
